creator: Sebastien BECKER
descriptionHtml:
- Mastermind -

What is Mastermind?
    The Mastermind game is a board game whose goal is to find a code.
    This Mastermind allows several configuration of levels for more difficulty.
    This Mastermind is a game of reflection, and of deduction on several levels of difficulties.

    Thanks to the different levels, the rules of the Mastermind can be easily adjusted to suit everyone.

What is the interest of the Mastermind?
    The goal of the Mastermind is to guess, by successive deductions, the color and the position of the 5 pawns hidden behind a screen. Beginners can adopt a less difficult formula by hiding only 3 or 4 pawns and using only 6 colors instead of 8.

How does a game of Mastermind work?
    The player fills the current line with colored chips.
    When validating the line, the number of pawns corresponds by its position and its color to a hidden pawn is indicated by a value in the black circle. The number of pawns corresponds only by its color is indicated in the white circle.

Subject related to the Mastermind
    Classified as a board game and a puzzle game, it is also a strategy game.
    It is also a game whose secret code has to be discovered. This makes Mastermind, too, a deduction and puzzle game.
    For children, it is an awakening game, a classic game for children and for the family

thanks
     Thank you for installing and playing with this Mastermind.

If you have any questions about this Mastermind, please don't hesitate to contact us via sbecker.app@gmail.com
descriptionShort: Mastermind is an exciting strategy and puzzle game. Challenge your self !
